354
00:18:46,668 --> 00:18:47,920
Eu comecei a briga.

355
00:18:48,003 --> 00:18:50,339
Ele não precisava
ter terminado.

356
00:18:50,422 --> 00:18:52,341
SR. VAN ZANDT:
Liberty?

357
00:18:56,637 --> 00:18:57,513
Oi, Danny.

358
00:18:57,596 --> 00:18:58,305
Onde está sua irmã?

359
00:18:59,765 --> 00:19:00,849
Reunião do grêmio estudantil.

360
00:19:00,933 --> 00:19:01,850
Ela já foi embora.

361
00:19:01,934 --> 00:19:03,060
SR. VAN ZANDT:
Ah, é?

362
00:19:03,143 --> 00:19:07,105
